ness creators<br\/><br\/>• Entrepreneurs<br\/><br\/>• Daily hydration routines<\/p><p>Zero sugar. No dyes. Portable. Customizable.<\/p>","text_style":"body"}},"button_FH4hWR":{"type":"button","disabled":true,"settings":{"button_label":"Shop Now","button_link":"shopify:\/\/collections\/all","button_style_secondary":false}}},"block_order":["heading_nfB6Up","text_t7LdWp","button_FH4hWR"],"name":"Image with text v1","settings":{"page_width":true,"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/5_1.jpg","mob_image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/5_1.jpg","contain":true,"cstm_padding":false,"height":"adapt","desktop_image_width":"medium","layout":"text_first","image_behavior":"none","content_layout":"no-overlap","desktop_content_position":"middle","desktop_content_alignment":"left","mobile_content_alignment":"left","section_color_scheme":"scheme-ae97f25d-9687-4460-bed4-d305a652f713","color_scheme":"scheme-ae97f25d-9687-4460-bed4-d305a652f713","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0,"margin_top":40,"margin_bottom":40}},"image_with_text_v1_XtE6Tg":{"type":"image-with-text-v1","blocks":{"heading_eWbKXg":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"WHO THIS IS FOR","heading_size":"h0"}},"text_PkexdY":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Built for Communities That Care About Health<\/p><p>Hydra performs especially well with creators in:<\/p><p>• Moms and parenting<br\/><br\/>• Youth sports families<br\/><br\/>• GLP-1 and weight loss<br\/><br\/>• Breastfeeding support<br\/><br\/>• Senior wellness and caregivers<br\/><br\/>• Fitness and pilates<br\/><br\/>• Beauty and skin<br\/><br\/>• Wellness and clean living<br\/><br\/>• Hangover recovery<br\/><br\/>• Lifestyle creators<\/p><p>If your audience cares about feeling better, Hydra fits naturally.<\/p>","text_style":"body"}},"button_7N6LEe":{"type":"button","disabled":true,"settings":{"button_label":"Shop Now","button_link":"shopify:\/\/collections\/all","button_style_secondary":false}}},"block_order":["heading_eWbKXg","text_PkexdY","button_7N6LEe"],"name":"