ries do I have?","ans_content":"<p>Entries are shown on each product page, so you always know what you're earning as you shop.<\/p>"}},"question_67B8mN":{"type":"question","settings":{"quest":"When is the giveaway period?","ans_content":"<p>Monday, September 8th @ 8:00 am PST - December 2nd @ 11:59 pm PST.<\/p>"}},"question_9txdF4":{"type":"question","settings":{"quest":"How is the winner contacted?","ans_content":"<p>The winner will be contacted directly on or around December 12, 2025.<br\/>We will never ask you for information or money to collect your prize.<\/p>"}},"question_p8DTfj":{"type":"question","settings":{"quest":"How do I claim my prize?","ans_content":"<p>After the winner is contacted, you will be able to choose the package or $100,000. After you fill out the proper legal paperwork, which we will provide, you can make your decision.<\/p>"}},"question_8fpWDk":{"type":"question","settings":{"quest":"When is the winner announced?","ans_content":"<p>The winner will be announced on or around December 17, 2025.<\/p>"}},"question_3BAVGc":{"type":"question","settings":{"quest":"Who is Shared Sweeps?","ans_content":"<p>Shared Sweeps is a shared giveaway platform that partners with brands (Like Hydra Pops) to enable their customers to earn entries to the giveaway for purchasing on their site!<\/p>"}},"question_7CfVDE":{"type":"question","settings":{"quest":"Is there a free method of entry?","ans_content":"<p>Yes! Please check the official rules for the details on the free method of entry.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["question_K4hfEk","question_LzJ8gU","question_67B8mN","question_9txdF4","question_p8DTfj","question_8fpWDk","question_3BAVGc","question_7CfVDE"],"disabled":true,"name":"FAQ accordions","settings":{"heading":"Questions? We can help!","caption":"","desc":"","btn-label":"","btn-link":"","color_scheme_faqbox":"scheme-1","color_scheme":"","padding_top":40,"padding_bottom":40,"padding_top_mob":28,"padding_bottom_mob":0}},"rich_text_7JQKRr":{"type":"rich-text","